","msg":"火車我覺得硬卧夠做<br />\n如果你4個人又想安心d,就軟卧，有間有門既房，同4張床<br />\n同埋早30日可以上網買飛<br />\n<br />\n利申：今年年頭深圳到拉薩，響西寧轉加氧車"},{"pid":"ed9c0e9dba374b24970851632900c13c07f39380","tid":453174,"uid":71531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:50:12.000Z","msg":"已買機票 23/12去到1/1<br />\n想問下使唔使book定住宿同包車拼車果方面點?<br />\n聯絡左一個司機但好似開得幾貴下"},{"pid":"95e66e6ecfcf802f4e692fa7f008234224e78fd1","tid":453174,"uid":90473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已買機票 23/12去到1/1<br />\n想問下使唔使book定住宿同包車拼車果方面點?<br />\n聯絡左一個司機但好似開得幾貴下</blockquote><br />\n幾錢？個司機咩名"},{"pid":"bdd1e9acd15825ad121935cb3f33923114273c10","tid":453174,"uid":145148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已買機票 23/12去到1/1<br />\n想問下使唔使book定住宿同包車拼車果方面點?<br />\n聯絡左一個司機但好似開得幾貴下</blockquote><br />\n我都有興趣 呢個時間去"},{"pid":"514311c4143679211ec4b03c8f9c43eea9fddd0f","tid":453174,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3dc5a836fdce4f955113fe3051f6b3fad7e2977d","tid":453174,"uid":118652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"我3-4月有冇人跟"},{"pid":"66ce8fd9b7fe1dcccd5c5aacca7db42b216b15c7","tid":453174,"uid":12104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我3-4月有冇人跟</blockquote><br />\n我frd 話4 月會好啲，諗緊好唔好4月去，你諗住去幾多日？ 如果你4月去可以跟"},{"pid":"e5b6f7202b2047c33c071cea19bf9928ea7c1636","tid":453174,"uid":14566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"睇你諗住去邊姐<br />\n如果係林芝果d唔會有問題<br />\n珠鋒大本營都可以去，純粹無得過夜<br />\n<br />\n但係應該真係好撚凍，我夏天去都覺要著羽絨"},{"pid":"59b8d80b44648ba344fb5dfbbf0a226a95b5d052","tid":453174,"uid":68093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"一齊去漠河啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a8f8af22349d7575ab4d4d14b9c303760804bd","tid":453174,"uid":22439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你諗住去邊姐<br />\n如果係林芝果d唔會有問題<br />\n珠鋒大本營都可以去，純粹無得過夜<br />\n<br />\n但係應該真係好撚凍，我夏天去都覺要著羽絨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5月去大本營都好撚凍"},{"pid":"c8ac1370b9220b12d9ce1a1c51f1195b3ab51775","tid":453174,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出年三月尾去<br />\n諗緊需唔需要買goretex外套上珠峰大本營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟比較少去呢類地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚買返嚟五年內著得兩三次goretex物質就失效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇去過的巴絲有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3月我唔知啦<br />\n我一月頭上<br />\n著左superwarm 加面衫 有加冷衫加羽絨<br />\n都有少少凍 但忍得到<br />\n真正仆街既係手指同腳指<br />\n著2對襪加靴 腳指凍到無曬知覺<br />\n要不停上返車</blockquote><br />\n一月頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最凍嗰陣<br />\n你講個情況喺珠峰？</blockquote><br />\n珠峰<br />\n同納木措<br />\n屌那星<br />\n我凍到腳指無曬知覺<br />\n有條大陸仔除曬衫裸跑拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇著保暖襪嗰啲<br />\n諗緊著普普通通一對入門級行山鞋夠唔夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人建議 預定著2對<br />\n市區無野既 拉薩其實感覺凍香港少少咁<br />\n但去到特別凍既地方 好似珠峰 納木措 都有野保暖<br />\n如果去到有高山反應<br />\n好似去林芝個頭玩幾日先<br />\n林芝個度d叫做西藏既江南 風景唔錯 2000幾米高 仲低過拉薩<br />\n可以幫助適應</blockquote><br />\n我同fd冇咁多假了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係去埋林芝都okay<br />\n只可以包六日車去羊湖納木錯珠峰<br />\n留三四日喺拉薩適應</blockquote><br />\n拉薩真係識應留兩日都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正適應到就自然適應到"},{"pid":"e8fc333b393e47f04eaad9df3c503e9011ae946b","tid":453174,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T22:31:40.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f35c1dce0b6dfad2fc8a542bd7c0a47d98dea801","tid":453174,"uid":118652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我3-4月有冇人跟</blockquote><br />\n我frd 話4 月會好啲，諗緊好唔好4月去，你諗住去幾多日？ 如果你4月去可以跟</blockquote><br />\n10-12日"},{"pid":"d65a096f9f52f3c497c16ecbfcbca0f759e9de6d","tid":453174,"uid":85307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"here<br />\n凍到仆街"},{"pid":"a6448cb24b02ef48ec3b06c6d2fd9e125d392152","tid":453174,"uid":150693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n巴打係點去拉撒 直飛定係鐵路上<br />\n好想去珠峰大本營見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我坐火車去 <br />\n飛機返<br />\n然後住青年旅舍同人地拼車</blockquote><br />\n直接由廣州坐火車上去？</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n去到北京過對面月台轉車<br />\n諗住去個時好精力 感受下<br />\n<br />\n返黎就成都轉機</blockquote><br />\n我見啲人推介西寧再青藏上去廿幾個鐘好似又快又靚<br />\n巴打搭咗2日？</blockquote><br />\n嚴格黎講係3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最恐怖係去廁所<br />\n強國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但聽人講依程火車票最難買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽聞好多黃牛飛，俾旅行社包哂賣俾鬼佬，所以西寧站會見到一堆堆鬼佬上火車"},{"pid":"f36cb549d4789602110ed021b65a855fd1816c97","tid":453174,"uid":150693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無<br />\n果時七月去 一早一晚都好撚凍<br />\n但係堅靚 值得去既<br />\n未去過的話，最好去之前一個月開始食紅景天supplement</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者食西藥Diamox，聽返d feedback都有效過紅景天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但西藥始終多副作用，利尿、手腳少麻痺<br />\n利申：五月去西藏，係珠峰大本營訓左一晚，三個都食Diamox，零高反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e7b0f3e822cbb89c9a0374b6c26ed6c17cfc19","tid":453174,"uid":54028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"12月聖誕去過 有上珠峰大本營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a231b43826b66bc5c08ee8d73bbe3a2dc1bc82","tid":453174,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:33:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人有咁嘅經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住1月去14日 上網搵過都好有人係冬天去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有經驗 或者純粹去過西藏 又或者可能同期去嘅 都可以留個tg交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1bf2566b3a0bba78f5cc12a86a2087d43588306f","tid":453174,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:35:16.000Z","msg":"都係諗住一月頭去喎，玩兩個禮拜到"},{"pid":"580f00419ed9eec8501e0ef3f63a06918e13be3e","tid":453174,"uid":2317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:51:10.000Z","msg":"其實去拉薩玩多幾日會仲開心過你包架車去景點，去啲青年旅舍搵人一齊玩下歡樂好多，果啲咩大環線乜今線坐車用你九成時間，落車影相就下一站，第一日靚，但去多幾日你會寧願係城到周圍玩下，去左幾次既經驗黎，今年年中都有去過，有當地既朋友，我地4個人夾埋100蚊就有4人房，好抵玩、仲要靚過大部份旅館。<br />\n另外建議來回都搭飛機，因為寧願早啲到步，預多兩日係拉薩，好過你坐兩日車好辛苦咁上到去，都仲要預一日黎適應，而且坐車上去其實好悶，又唔平，遇到仆街同房就大撚鑊"},{"pid":"aa1d62752e4ce411b2dbd7ed1b72f910e55c9d3a","tid":453174,"uid":2317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:52:23.000Z","msg":"果啲紅景硬果啲其實作用唔大，你去到當地問啲司機叫佢地帶你買藥好過，果啲藥就真係好work"},{"pid":"c9c282bb536feb298f7235abe98d69b9f6259dd0","tid":453174,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實去拉薩玩多幾日會仲開心過你包架車去景點，去啲青年旅舍搵人一齊玩下歡樂好多，果啲咩大環線乜今線坐車用你九成時間，落車影相就下一站，第一日靚，但去多幾日你會寧願係城到周圍玩下，去左幾次既經驗黎，今年年中都有去過，有當地既朋友，我地4個人夾埋100蚊就有4人房，好抵玩、仲要靚過大部份旅館。<br />\n另外建議來回都搭飛機，因為寧願早啲到步，預多兩日係拉薩，好過你坐兩日車好辛苦咁上到去，都仲要預一日黎適應，而且坐車上去其實好悶，又唔平，遇到仆街同房就大撚鑊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄間旅舍叫咩名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4aecc46268ba7a47175ecc770496bbcdd3efc1f","tid":453174,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:11:51.000Z","msg":"準備7月去<br />\n留名睇下有冇平司機平旅舍"},{"pid":"000518405d73d3afab8a2d47e31db45593e38a7c","tid":453174,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T20:18:24.000Z","msg":"8月去完，建議食西藥，不過係上到去覺得有事先食會好啲，因為倚賴咗之後就好辛苦。我冇食過藥，同行友人就一直keep住食。我嗰陣第一日就沖凍水涼，同埋有日上到5千幾海拔跑步都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5355231461fe32c54d214a4fd7a101f818a488cb","tid":453174,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8月去完，建議食西藥，不過係上到去覺得有事先食會好啲，因為倚賴咗之後就好辛苦。我冇食過藥，同行友人就一直keep住食。我嗰陣第一日就沖凍水涼，同埋有日上到5千幾海拔跑步都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西藥係咪嗰隻Diamox？ 洗唔洗要醫生開架？"},{"pid":"8db8ecafebc9454444a7e0b6846f7c2cd6adf485","tid":453174,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"前幾年3月定4月去過珠峰大本營，果時啱啱過咗冬天開放返，好記得第2朝床隔離杯水結咗冰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedbe640dcdbd0334a27906e01248069b70fca5d","tid":453174,"uid":135081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"有無師兄黎緊1月都去西藏say個hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739af1518d174c38e3d73f6636e609656c66f27b","tid":453174,"uid":158117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"我同fd都會去阿 仲搵緊人夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來4人去但俾2個放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喊出黎<br />\n有興趣可以留低tg傾"},{"pid":"603b2005deff4bb63a236382b24fbf5780186e73","tid":453174,"uid":90473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":